nodes.text: Settlement 32 was a SELCORE refugee camp on Duro in 26 ABY. It contained Ryn, Vors, and Vuvrians. Its administrator was Han Solo, who was assisted by his son Jacen and the Ryn Droma. Settlement 32 was destroyed by naotebe winglings, insects created by Nom Anor that ate the domes of the camp, shortly before the Battle of Duro.
